<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Couple1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Couple,</orth> subst., 1) a tie that holds dogs together: <cit><quote>I'll go in --s with her,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 135</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) two, a brace: <cit><quote>a c. of Ford's knaves,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 99</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.5.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 5, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 44</bibl>.
<lb />3) a male and female joined: <cit><quote>this young c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 1, 40</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.202.40" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 202</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.186" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. IV, 1, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.414.186" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 414</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.36" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.242" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 242</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 134</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 134</bibl>

